OL,3,C'He gave me a job and a room and took
OL,4,Cmy money'
OL,6,FOur reporter Jonny Blair has been
OL,7,Finvestigating.
OL,9,FA victim of modern slavery has told
OL,10,Fhow he was exploited by someone who
OL,11,Foffered him a job before forcing him
OL,12,Fto hand over most of the money he made.
OL,14,FAron (not his real name) was later
OL,15,Fable to break free of the situation
OL,16,Fand get help.
