OL,3,C'He gave me a job and a room and took
OL,4,Cmy money'
OL,6,FHe told ITV Tyne Tees he was
OL,7,Fbefriended by a man who offered him a
OL,8,Froom and a job after he came to the UK
OL,9,Fseeking asylum. He'd been persecuted
OL,10,Ffor his sexuality in his home country.
OL,12,FWhile waiting for his application to
OL,13,Fbe processed, he took an offer of work
OL,14,Fand found himself forced to hand over
OL,15,Fmost of the money he made.
OL,17,F"I didn't know it would be like that,"
OL,18,Fhe said.
