OL,3,C'He gave me a job and a room and took
OL,4,Cmy money'
OL,6,F"Even before this guy offered me a job
OL,7,Fhe didn't tell me anything about how
OL,8,Fhe would take the money. He said 'you
OL,9,Fcan just give me a little.'... But
OL,10,Flater on he started saying two
OL,11,Fdifferent things.
OL,13,F"I started realising that this money,
OL,14,Fwhen I'm working, it's not helping me.
OL,15,FIt's not doing anything... That guy
OL,16,Flater on started asking me for a lot
OL,17,Fof money sometimes."
