OL,6,FEventually Aron, whose identity is
OL,7,Fbeing protected, ended up sleeping
OL,8,Frough before being referred to the
OL,9,FSalvation Army for help.
OL,11,FWhat is modern slavery?
OL,13,FModern slavery refers to a person
OL,14,Fbeing used by a criminal - or
OL,15,Fcriminals - for their own gain. They
OL,16,Fmay be threatened, forced or coerced
OL,17,Finto practices like forced labour,
OL,18,Fcrime, sexual exploitation or domestic
OL,19,Fservitude.
