OL,3,C'He gave me a job and a room and took
OL,4,Cmy money'
OL,6,FIn the North East, between June 2023
OL,7,Fand June 2024, 223 people were
OL,8,Freferred to Salvation Army as victims
OL,9,Fof modern slavery.
OL,11,FThis represents a decrease of 8%
OL,12,Fcompared to the previous year. It
OL,13,Freflects the wider figures for England
OL,14,Fand Wales which show, for the first
OL,15,Ftime in 13 years, a decrease in the
OL,16,Fnumber of people coming forward to
OL,17,Faccess support (by 22%).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
