OL,4,Cmy money'
OL,6,FHowever, according to the charity
OL,7,Fbehind the numbers, The Salvation
OL,8,FArmy, this is not due to the problem
OL,9,Freducing. Rather it reflects the fact
OL,10,Fthat victims are becoming more and
OL,11,Fmore scared to ask for help.
OL,13,FSigns of modern slavery include:
OL,15,F'Low risk, high reward'
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/11
