OL,3,C'He gave me a job and a room and took
OL,4,Cmy money'
OL,6,FThe Salvation Army is one of the
OL,7,Fleading providers of support for
OL,8,Faffected adults. It says the number of
OL,9,Fpeople being helped still remains much
OL,10,Flower compared to those trapped in
OL,11,Fexploitation.
OL,13,FA report produced by the charity found
OL,14,Fmodern slavery remains a "low risk,
OL,15,Fhigh reward" activity for criminals.
OL,17,FThe charity has several safe house
OL,18,Facross the region, where it helps
OL,19,Fvictims to rehabilitate and recover.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
