OL,3,C'He gave me a job and a room and took
OL,4,Cmy money'
OL,6,FCraig Hilton, from the charity, said:
OL,7,F"The individuals we support lose
OL,8,Feverything; their identity, who they
OL,9,Fare, where they've come from.
OL,10,FTortured. Really exploited to the
OL,11,Fpoint where they're just a commodity.
OL,13,F"They're valuable to the exploiters
OL,14,Fbut that's it. It's all about greed
OL,15,Fand getting as much money as they can
OL,16,Ffrom individuals. And when they're
OL,17,Fspent, so to speak, they are literally
OL,18,Fdiscarded like you would a packet of
OL,19,Fcrisps or something. It's that
OL,20,Fflippant, unfortunately."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/11
