OL,3,C'He gave me a job and a room and took
OL,4,Cmy money'
OL,6,FThe charity - and its partners - have
OL,7,Fhelped nearly 25,000 victims over the
OL,8,Flast 13 years.
OL,10,FHowever, for the first time in that
OL,11,Fperiod, the number of people being
OL,12,Fhelped has fallen, across England and
OL,13,FWales (June 2023 - June 2024 figures).
OL,15,FThe charity puts the drop, largely,
OL,16,Fdown to recent changes tightening
OL,17,Fimmigration laws. It says a subsequent
OL,18,Fconflation between modern slavery and
OL,19,Fimmigration is making victims scared
OL,20,Fto come forward, fearful of being
OL,21,Fdeported or detained.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/11
