OL,6,FA Home Office spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Modern slavery has devastating
OL,8,Fimpacts and the new government is
OL,9,Fcommitted to tackling this heinous
OL,10,Fcrime in all its forms.
OL,12,F"We constantly keep our policies under
OL,13,Freview in order to best protect
OL,14,Fvictims and ensure they are working
OL,15,Fefficiently and effectively."
